{
  "stem": "4189.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We of course, we didn't know this in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know their intention.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We thought that they would really send those people to Germany to work there, and because the war was going on, and all the German males were in the army, and they needed the workers.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So after we found out though that nobody was coming back and that they didn't get any mail from them, nobody applied anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So what they did then, they rounded up people in the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What they would do, they would take combat trucks with soldiers and they would surround a whole area, like a two block area, surround it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then make a search, house by house, and take all the young males at first, and take them in and arrest them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in June, on June 13 of 1942, I was caught in such an action.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what they did with us, they only took young men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at that time, I was 16, I believe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took us all, put us-- brought us to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they shipped us to France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They sent us to France to Boulogne-sur-Mer, near a town, it's called Condete.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's spelled C-O-N-D-E-T-E.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Condete.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And over there they dropped, they dropped off some tents, large tents, and some lumber.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, here, build a camp, and you're going to stay here and work here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the guards that supervised this camp was from the organization Todt, which was also a Nazi organization, similar to the SS.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These guys were-- they wore brown uniforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were like a, I don't know, like an army engineering corp, something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They used to do the building and construction, like roadwork, and this kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
